code> here?</li>\n<li>it requires as an input an instance of <code>i ∈ s</code>. I know I should have this since the sum is written <code>∑ i ∈ s, ...</code>, but I don't seem to have access to this assertion with <code>conv</code>. how do I get access to <code>i ∈ s</code>?</li>\n</ol>",
